Author: Marwan K.
Content: This is really delicious burger I tried 5 and 10 they both really goodeverything in the place is just awesome The services the design and the people who works their

Author: Barbara B.
Content: Very enjoyable burger  This place is more about the toppings and less about the meat  The meat patty is thin which allows the toppings to shine  I had the burger with onion strings and blue cheese  I enjoyed it but not as much as my burger at the Butcher and the Burger  I just like biting into a big juicy burger which I did not get here    Atmosphere is warm and kind of funky pretty loud inside   Had to shout to hear my date  Minus a star for the sweet potato fries they were really disappointing with a light lemon aioli that I did not at all care for  Would try one of the other fries

Author: Jesse T.
Content: Very creative burgers The accessories fries shakes mac and cheese could be a successful restaurant on their own without the outstanding meat but Im glad theyre together hereThe beer list is very good and the waitstaff are great The place gets crowded and loud when the weekend rolls around but its worth the wait

Author: Tiffany R.
Content: Service was amazingly great  Effie is super cool I admit I am vegetarian so I only got a veggie burger which was good They have a good number of beers and Effie will help you find the beer of your liking I will be back with my meat eating friends

Author: Chelsea B.
Content: Well I decided that since I have never ordered anything other then the lamb burger that I should branch out a bit The last 2 times I visited DMK I ordered different things I can happily say that the patty melt and the burger with the blueberry BBQ sauce are both just as amazing at the lamb This is great and unfortunate news Because now it will make deciding what to get much more difficult

Author: Bridgid R.
Content: The 6 is the best burger ever but the Parmesan fries rocked too  This is my new favorite burger joint

Author: Kassidy D.
Content: I had the lamb burger and was really pleased The bun tasted fresh It was delicious as were the Wisconsin cheddar and scallion fries The service was great and it seemed like a really great place to go and hang out I went with 3 people on a Monday and had no problem with a wait It wasnt overpriced at all I would definitely recommend

Author: Tues T.
Content: Oh YES These burgers are GOOD so are the friesThe BIG salad isnt that big 3 adults shared the salad 2 orders of fries Parmesan Truffle Cream and the Amish Blue  Smoked Bacon and we each got a burger PERFECT Also LOVED the pineapple basil soda

Author: Justin G.
Content: Great burger fun atmosphere  They have a rewards program which is nice  Honestly my second favorite burger in the city but the reality is it comes down to preference between DMK and Kumas my wife likes DMK better

Author: Emily H.
Content: Amazing milk shakes I got the smore shake and it tastes just like a toasted marshmallow I had the bartender add khalua and it was great

Author: Colleen T.
Content: Ill keep it short and sweet Not the best burger Ive ever eaten but definitely top 10 opt for their special burgers because you never you what youre going to miss out on let me skip to the part I really care abouttheir fries Im not just talking about the stupid potatoes but I AM going to rave about the truffle sauce it comes with seriously people please have a warning on the menu that states these fries may cause an orgasmic reaction now granted Im pretty sure this is my first time Ive had truffle oil anything but holy shit it was like losing my virginity again that is all have a nice day

Author: Christina L.
Content: Honestly it was okay We went on a double lunch date here with some pals last week and it was good but not worth the hype The couple we went with ordered the salmon burger as well as the 5 bison burger with blueberry bbq sauce  They ordered off the segment from Diners drive ins and dives The bison burger was up to par and was a good burger but we agreed not as good as kumas The salmon burger was shared by my friend and I and truthfully it was a let down On triple D Guy was talking it up and when i got it it was almost overwhelming fishy and way to strong on the curry aiolli We both had a few bites but were dissatisfied with how strong the curry wasOur boyfriends enjoyed their burgers the bison burger and the patty melt My boyfriend upgraded his patty melt to a double and added a fried egg and he loved it The only complaint was the plates were too small for such a messy burger To my dissatisfaction of my salmon burger he ordered me the milkshake off the day a toasted marshmallow milkshake That was simply the best milkshake of my life We also got the cheddar fries to share and they were good but just standard merits cheddar with scallions But they were still good Overall I would go to a different burger joint before this place again It wasnt horrible by any means but it just wasnt worth all the hype

Author: Kate U.
Content: I am a fan of DMK Burger bar  Everyone knows this place from its reputation and from Diners Driveins and Dives  There are definitely some GREAT things about this place  The burgers are probably the most unique burgers you will ever have in your life  I highly recommend the blueberry bbq sauce I know it sounds weird but trust me its really good  The burger buns are very different and something you wont have anywhere else it truly is a gourmet burger  The burger melts in your mouth they are able to do something so unique and bring out a ton of different flavorsThe fries are amazing as well they arent your typical standard fries and there are a variety of different types They complement the burger really well  In my experience the servers have always been really knowledgeable and helpful in telling you exactly what is on each burger and helping you make a decisionHowever the below is what keeps me from giving 5 stars  You cant customize your burger really in any way  for example I would LOVE lettuce  tomato on the 2 but you cant add it    Fries do not come with the burger you need to pay for them separately  This makes the bill so much higher because who doesnt get fries with a burger  Also they come in a really large size when you order them so a lot of them end up going to waste at the end  Anyways this is probably the best gourmet burger Ive ever had I just wish that for the price that you pay they would give you fries with it and let you somewhat customize the burgers

Author: J D.
Content: Awesome experience 4 burger with green chilis fried egg and bacon on fresh made bun was fantastic Cheddar and scallion fries were great and marshmallow milkshake was delicious Service was fast and very nice Best burger experience ever

Author: Amanda W.
Content: Delicious burgers I had the 2 as a turkey burger Perfect size deliciously juicy burger I also kind of love that you can only delete ingredients not substitute Had the sweet potato fries with lemon Tabasco aioli yum Very enjoyable atmosphere but it is in the loud side

Author: Mark M.
Content: My girlfriend and I visited last night after hearing about DMK through Diners Driveins and Dives We stopped by on a Saturday evening at about 800pm  the place was rockin We waited about 2030 minutes at the bar and then were seated The beer list offers terrific options and the bar serves some nice cocktails The food was excellent and memorable I had the 1 burger with cheddar bacon and BBQ sauce and my gf had the salmon burger We shared and both were outstanding We also enjoyed the salt and pepper fries with tasty spicy house ketchup Pricewise DMK was moderate Its not a cheap meal but not crazy expensive either Our meal of two burgers fries and a round of beer was under 50 with tip The only downside of the evening was the service which was a bit slow We waited for another round of beers for too long so thats what keeps this review from being 5 starsWell likely return and would definitely recommend DMK Burger Bar to other foodies that love a great burger and a lively ambiance

Author: Chris V.
Content: Amazing burger and great fries If you dont want a big meal I highly recommend coming here after your first few drinks and going to the bar and getting some fries split them between two people enjoy a beer and move on

Author: Gina S.
Content: I love DMK  Very good burger GREAT fries nice servers  It is my stand by burger place in the city  After my last Kumas experience I will be at DMK much more  You cannot go wrong with anything on their menu

Author: Michelle B.
Content: DMK is my go to burger joint  One thing I love about this place is the portion size  The burgers and fries are not ridiculously big like Kumas or lockdown  It is also big enough that I leave feeling full  I have had almost every burger on the menu and they are all fantastic  My favorites are the 7 big DMK burger or the 13 crispy portobello  All the fries are great as well but I always order the blue cheese and bacon or parmesan truffle cream  Not only is everything on the menu amazing they also have a great alcohol selection  If you are looking for a nice laid back burger joint with great drinks at a reasonable price I highly recommend DMK

Author: Mike A.
Content: Hands down the tastiest burgers in town if are in the mood for gourmet burgers  oxymoron but they pull it off wellThis is good in a non five guys kind of wayits a more refined combination of flavours  the blue cheese chipotle burger is amazingI have been here at least a dozen times and really like the vibe just note that it can get a little loud which makes it hard to talk overBeyond that always a consistent treat Truffle fries sea salt and black pepper fries and Wisconsin cheddar are a must

Author: Britt C.
Content: Someone has to review the veggie burger right  Well it was fantastic  Nice chew and didnt fall apart  The bun was truly what set this apart from other burgers however  It was so soft and fluffy but REAL  Definitely not a sticky enriched white bread bunThis was one of those times when I wish I drank liquor because the cocktail list looked great with a nice mix of herbal and real fruit offerings  But the beer list was commendable and that always goes with a burgerFInally the fries  They have a varied selection of handcut fries all of which looked great  We went with the sweet potato fries that came with tabascolemon dip and the parmesantruffle fries which were amazing  I might go back just for fries and boozeFun clean atmosphere  I will be back

Author: Rick T.
Content: Maybe Im just done with this whole burger thing or maybe my expectations are too highSo yeah This is a burger joint where the fries taste exactly like 99 of the other places that slice potatoes and throw them into hot oil for 3 minutesI got an entrylevel burger which came topped with cheddar and pickled onions My first impression Shouldnt a burger bar give you a BURGER  I mean you know a real manly halfpound minimum burger DMK gives youspitballing herea onethird pound burger that doesnt exactly hide but certainly doesnt dominate the sandwich If I want a pussy boy burger Id go to a pussy boy burger place Gimme a goddam BURGEROn top of that DMK deploys one of my leastfavorite restaurant practices in the whole world They sell soft drinks by the can in a waiterservice restaurant and charge you for each one Thats crap If I want to overpay for soft drinks at a restaurant Ill go to like Brazzaz where they sell 8ounce bottles for 3 a piece while I chomp on an endless supply of intentionally oversalted meatOh right How was did the burger taste Like a burger with a little too much bun The picked onions were good

Author: Jacob H.
Content: Favorite burger spot Fries are great  Shakes are great Burgers are great Atmosphere is great Even the drinks are great Get a DMK card to earn some points I earned my dmk shirt and it is sooo comfy Oh yeah No 5 no 7 No 1 add bacon Dang Everything is good Enjoy

Author: Leah C.
Content: Apparently Im the minority not the first time but I was less than impressed by DMK Burger Bar  With SO many options for delicious burgers throughout the city I expected great things from a place with Burger Bar in the nameFirst lets discuss the drinks  I ordered Respect Your Elders and unfortunately it tasted syrupy and extremely artificial  My boyfriend ordered The Smash and while it was drinkable it wasnt memorableSo back to those burgers  Maybe my expectations were unfounded but I was SHOCKED by the size of the burgers  Do not go here if youre looking to bite into a big juicy burger a la Butcher  The Burger  In fact my experience gave me exactly the opposite  a small thin slightly dry patty  Consider your expectations forewarnedMy fondest memory of the meal would definitely be the fries  As a table we ordered the Sweet Potato Fries Parmesan Truffle Cream fries and Wisconsin Cheddar  Scallion fries  They were all pretty darn delicious  Theyre cut a little on the smallerthin side so dont expect any wedges or steak fries but the seasonings and dips are quite tastyAll in all a decent place but I didnt think it lived up to the hype  Id only go back if someone else was dying to go there

Author: Mark C.
Content: So my fiancee Sara finally moved in last weekend   An exciting but exhausting day left us in the evening wanting to take a much needed break  from moving from wedding planning from kitchen planning and what better way to take a break than to hit up one of our favorite spots  DMK burger bar  We got there around 6pm on a Saturday night and luckily was able to snag a table within 15 or 20 minutesDMK Burger Bar was the first of many joint projects from restauranteur David Morton and chef Michael Kornick and while it seems like it was just recently that it opened up DMK has been a fixture in Lakeview for almost 5 years nowTo start we got an order of the fried pickles and okra the pickles extremely sweet and flavorful Sara took most of the okra but I snagged a piece  cut in longitundinal slices as opposed to the usual crosswise gives it a different texture  And who doesnt love ranch with anything fried4  Fried Egg hatched green chile sonoma jack Smoked BaconFor a goto burger the 4 is one of my favorites  While Im beginning to think that a burger with a fried egg doesnt really need any cheese on it the sonoma jack here gets a bit lost  Not that its a bad thing  The flavorful well cooked burger mixes perfectly with the fried egg and the fresh buns soften up as it soaks up the egg yolk   The green chile adds just the right amount of spice to the stack  And I think one of the best parts about DMK is that they dont overpile the ingredients and they dont try to do too much again a la Kumas  And as tempting as it to upgrade to a double I held some restraintShrimp burger ginger cilantro sesame ginger slawSara went with the shrimp burger  the special 15  She loved it so much I didnt get much of a taste but with one bite I could tell this was a keeper  Very original very tasty  her wordsFor sides we went with fries over mac and cheese  got an order of sweet potato fries with a subtle lemon tabasco aioli and the fries with amish blue topped with smoked bacon  Neither was as good as their cheddar and scallion fries or their parmesan truffle but both were solid  The sweet potato fries were well cooked but not as crisp as I would have liked and the lemon mayo was pretty subtle and didnt add much  The blue cheese and bacon fries were heavily topped and the blue cheese doesnt spread well and makes it a bit difficult to scoop up the ingredients but its a solid dishBased on the quality of the DMK Burger Bar you can see why the DMK empire is rapidly expanding  Good choices solid ingredients good atmosphere  The beer list is formidable and the have a decent selections of bourbon for a burger joint   Its not the place for massive appetites if youre looking for pure size go somewhere else but if you want a good solid wellsized burger DMK is a great optionpics and details on my blogeatinginchicago2014word…

Author: Jay S.
Content: DMK used to be one of my favorite burger bars but our experience last night dropped it completely off the scale for me Theyve done something new with how they salt and spice their burgers and its just bad I had the 8 and my cousin had the bison burger  neither one of us could taste the meat or toppings apart from the salty spice flavoring Way too overpowering And on a side note maybe Im getting too old but having to yell at the person across from me just to hear isnt that fun Id consider getting takeout from these guys if I were begged but other than that Im done with them

Author: Jim S.
Content: One of the better burgers I had ever had The atmosphere was a bit dark and loud but the food and beer selection were outstanding Highly recommend eating here

Author: Magen R.
Content: 5 stars for DMK This place is truly one of the gems in Lakeview as far as I am concerned I love everything about their food and every time I come Im overwhelmed with great choices so Ill review my most recent visit this past Saturday afternoon After a bit of mimosa fun a girlfriends who lives nearby we headed to DMK for some food and a beverage We were all pretty hungry so we started out with their macaroni and cheese which was simple but delicious as was evident by the three of us basically inhaling it in less than ten minutes For my meal I split the special a fried shrimp burger with one of my friends and we got the salt and pepper and sweet potato fries for the table Ive never had a shrimp burger before but DMK made me so glad I tried one It had just the right amount of crunch and had a great flavor As for the fries amazing They definitely take it to the next level with their awesome dipping sauces the lemony one that came with the sweet potato fries was outstanding and I loved the spicy ketchup that took their salt and pepper fries to the next level Ive never had a bad experience at DMK and I doubt I ever will its a great spot

Author: Sonya L.
Content: This is a cool place Modern decor nice and friendly servers huge burgers yummy cocktails  We ordered the onion straws and parmesan fries to get the meal started For vegans and vegetarians you should know the fries are fried in something with beef which our server was nice enough to inform us without asking  But thats a bit disappointing since it was one of the reasons I went to begin with  The Mac and cheese was very creamy which I love The veggie patty was fine with good texture and flavor  I highly recommend the Smash drink if you like mint as it was very refreshing  All in all a satisfying meal and I have nothing bad to say about the experience Id go back if I was in the mood for heavy food and friends were going but I wont go back on my own since I like fries with my veggie burger

Author: Abby H.
Content: Delicious burgers but the prices were really high considering you had to order fries separately The buns are made in house which is extra delicious

Author: Kori E.
Content: We came on a Wednesday night and we were quoted 30 minutes  I was shocked I dont think I realized it would be this busy We were seated within that time frame and everything came out super fast Our waitress was great but some substitutions that someone wanted to make to their burger were denied He wanted the lamb burger with a portabello mushroom on top  apparently this couldnt be done Why I dont know Another set back  they seemed to be out of a lot of stuff It was kinda weirdBUT  on to the food The burgers and fries and mac n cheese were fantastic I had the 1 and it was great The burgers are not huge which I prefer The truffle fries were my fave as were the blue cheese fries The portions are not all that large and for 5 people we devoured all of it We didnt have a problem with service so that was a plus I would definitely come back here  I dont know if I would wait 2 hours but I would come back

Author: Luis O.
Content: Although the taste is good I was disappointed on the fact that the patties were rather thin We ordered an order of fries that came with cheese The cheese wasnt very good so we returned the fries They were pretty cool with taking it back and bringing us a different kind They also included a free blood orange soda for everyone at the table for our dissatisfaction The soda was freaking amazing I would recommend getting that drink

Author: Cait K.
Content: Let it be known how much I love DMK I love the new location in Evanston but this space is much larger and the menu more extensiveCame here on a whim with my fiance after seeing a show at Second City and it was hopping at 630 on a Saturday We elected to wait at the bar with drinks until our table was ready Their draft selection was pretty awesome Im a pale ale girl all the way and I had at least 4 options We were able to get seats and the service was friendly and promptWe got seated after about 25 fast minutes and I was SO pleased with our server He was really friendly in his interactions and pretty funny After a string of bad service recently it was really refreshing to go somewhere where the waiter actually seemed happy we were there He also brought us a shamrock shake to split at the end of our meal which was a really nice touch Im not super into mint milkshakes or dessert in general but I thought it was nicely done for what it was and the fiancee made quick work of both glasses Oh yeah he split it into two glasses for us SO NICEWe ordered the cheddar fries to share and they were amazing The scallions are a nice fresh touch to an otherwise pretty heavy item We seriously considered ordering the blue cheese fries too but decided we should save something for next time I ordered the lamb burger I pretty much order lamb anywhere its an option and it did not disappoint I loved the salty feta olive tapenade creamy tzatziki and crispy cucumbers as toppings I would definitely order this again My fiance ordered the big DMK and he loved it Hes a burger purist and this was the perfect option for him an elevated Big MacDelicious food great service and a good beer menu well be back

Author: Monica B.
Content: I loooove the bison burger  Meat is perfectly cooked and the blueberry bbq sauce goat cheese and pickled onions create for an amazing combination  The burgers here arent as ginormous as Kumas but they are just as deliciousIve sampled the chocolate shake which is also delicious  But the winner for me are the fries  I looove the parmesan with truffle cream  You need to eat these while theyre hot and freshThe rest of the menu looks great but I cant help but stick to my favorites

Author: Nida K.
Content: I really really liked my food hereI got the bison burger the 5 No complaintswe also got the parmesan fries sweet potato fries and the onion strings The first two were great the onion strings were only okay Too much breading not enough onionI want to come back here

Author: Lauren L.
Content: The place was crowded but we sat down quickly and just in time for the lunch rush The burgers were perfectly proportioned and cooked to perfection And then the fries for the table were the delicious We had no complaints at all and even received some free mixed shots from the bar just cause I would love to go back and try the parmesan fries and a bison burger well be back for sure

Author: Heather L.
Content: Best burger in the city For sure Dont even say the word Kuma Their veggie patties are also amazing The price is worth it for high quality food and chefquality flavor combos Try the salt and pepper fries or the Wisconsin cheddar Both are incredible It gets loud on weekend nights but its a fun place Go early and go often

Author: Taylor M.
Content: DMK Burger was awesome  It gives Kumas a run for its money  When we arrived on a Saturday night around 8 pm there was an hour wait for two people which is about what I expected  But we grabbed drinks at the bar and time passed quickly  By the time we were seated our tummies were grumbling enticed by the savory smellsOur eyes were bigger than our tummies so we ordered the blue cheese and bacon fries Mac and Cheese 2 Fried Okra and Pickles and each got a burger  The Mac and Cheese was just okay while everything else I ate was incredible  The fried okra and pickles were a great combination  The fries had a ton of cheese and bacon on top of them and were super rich  I ordered what I think was called the Chipotle Burger  It had guacamole and other deliciousness on it  Needless to say we were not able to finish everythingThe service was fabulous and the food was great  I am sure I will be back

Author: Linda B.
Content: I thought DMK Burger Bar was okay but Kumas is the gold standard and I couldnt help comparing the two  Really Im not sure that DMK BB was better than places like 25 Degrees or Big  Littles  There are just so many spots in Chicago to get a really good burger that I cant imagine going back to wait in line here againWe got to DMK BB around 630pm on Sat night and I was hoping that would be early enough to avoid a massive wait  No such luck  We had been waiting about 45 minutes when seats at the bar opened up and we grabbed them  I started with the DMK mojito with 10 cane rum  It was not bad but not good either  Something was off with the mixture maybe not enough sugar and the drink ended up being just okayI had burger 4 Roasted Hatch Green Chile Fried Farm Egg Sonoma Jack Smoked Bacon and I thought that the meat lacked seasoning  I also had macaroni and cheese 2 Gruyere Smoked Bacon Charred Balsamic Red Onionsagain it was just okay  The flavors werent particularly good or interesting by contrast I have been blown away by some of the mac and cheese combos at Kumas  The truffle and parmesan fries were very good thoughOn the whole Im glad I tried it but a return visit is unlikely

Author: Bryant H.
Content: The Burger I inhaled  was with aged cheddar smoked bacon charred balsamic red onions rufus teagues bbq sauce was on point The Parmesan Fries with truffle creamAmazing The customer service was great because I asked for the shamrock shake and they were out They gave me a free voucher to get the shake when it comes in the next day

Author: K R.
Content: Cool burger spot This was a cool experience The staff was very friendly and the atmosphere was laid back Our waiter JACK was awesome We tried 2 different burgers 2 different fries 3 different dipping sauce the mac and cheese and the peanut butter shake None of it was disappointing My 5yr old loved the fries and mac and cheese even though it was fancier than he normally gets it The burgers were great we will return

Author: Megan H.
Content: Fancy fancy burgers with a side of chill vibes  Ill definitely be back So happy the Goldplaited Gals told me about this placeperks of working down the street on Sheffield  plus I heard they have adult milkshakes Must try next time

Author: Bran G.
Content: Burgers beers and atmosphere are all 5 stars at DMK It is a crowded place so be prepared to wait but there is a long bar with an extensive beer and cocktail list good tunes and TVs giddy up on a bar stool and chill with your group For being so popular I didnt feel overcrowded or squeezed into a waiting area Burger was brilliant and grassfed which only semipaleo nerds like me care about Basically your cow was not given steroids or drugs in order to beef it up pun intended meaning you are not eating steroids or drugs Anyway I got the 5 Bison Burger and it was awesome The pickled onions and goat cheese were a great combo and the blueberry BBQ was not overly sweet but actually provided some tang Had sweet potato fries too which were delicious but I dont think you can go wrong with any of the fries on the menu Also head the chili of the day is always a sleeper that can knock your socks off

Author: Hallie K.
Content: Great burgers and at a good price but no create your own option if thats whats youre looking for We came in around 730 on a Friday night and sat down at the bar We had great service and we were lucky enough to receive 3 free samples We tried the rhubarb milkshake truffle fries and cheese fries which were all good in addition to the 2 burgers and onion strings that we ordered

Author: Siddharth M.
Content: DMK is brilliant Service is good beer is better and the food is brilliant I had Number 4 on the menu Roasted Hatch Green Chile Fried Farm Egg Sonoma Jack Smoked Bacon and boy was it hot The meat was supple and succulent and the combination with the fries was fantasticThumbs up

Author: Kayleigh M.
Content: I love DMK The food is amazing and the atmosphere is really relaxed and laid back Im not usually a gourmet burger kinda girl but I adore the bison burger with blueberry barbecue sauce and goat cheese My only complaint would be the lack of a normal burger on the menu sometimes Im in the mood for a nofrills cheeseburger I always make sure to order friesthey dont come included with your burger Its always an emotional struggle to choose between the parmesan fries with truffle cream or the sweet potato fries with lemon tabasco aioli Great beer menu too

Author: Elliott M.
Content: Head to toe a delicious meal Not enough great things to say about DMK I got their veggie burger and it was everything I hoped hot tasty and filling The topping combos are also todie for And the shamrock shake for St Patricks Day was out of this world good I finished it and immediately wanted another oneThe only negatives I have are that their fries arent vegetarian They do however have vegetarian onion straws and fried pickles which begs the question why

Author: Mary B.
Content: A common misconception is that I live at DMK Burger Bar Or that I live nearby in Lakeview  Slightly afraid to admit to the nice staff that I actually live in Hyde Park approximately 63 minutes away on CTA Theres a reason why I keep coming back to dine at this fabulous establishment Correction multiple reasons I have never tried a burger here that I wasnt thrilled with I was given the recommendation to come here by a good friend of mine He joined their softball team at one point because he visited there often enough This makes me feel slightly better about how often Im hereThis most recent visit I had the 1 The burger is topped with aged cheddar smoked bacon charred balsamic red onions  Rufus Teagues BBQ sauce Amazing I admit I am particularly fond of good BBQ sauce The Rufus Teagues variation knocked my socks off Combining the sweet aspects of the sauce with the savory flavors of the smoked bacon is brilliant As far as cheddar cheese goes the aged cheddar was delightfully melted and provided a necessary sharpness to the toppings of the burger The red onions were sautéed and complimented the rest of the toppings well although beware you may end up with a couple in your lap if you arent careful Other burger recommendations include the 11 which features a lamb patty and the 4 a classic combination of fried egg  bacon atop a savory burger But honestly you cant go wrong with any of the options My friend who was experiencing DMK for the first time went with the 4 and had difficulty controlling the yolk while eating the burger Side note she is in the need of a cowboy from Texas who can bridle both the fried egg on her burger and her wild untamed heartNow onto even more reasons why I basically live here the sides As a friend remarked during lunch on Sunday the burgers get you in the door but the fries keep you coming back My friends and I split three different sides on this visit The sea salt  black pepper fries are great and come with the house ketchup The sweet potato fries come with a lemon tobasco aioli which is delicious Combining the bitter citrus taste of lemon with the richness of the sweet potatoes is bizarre but amazing The fried okra and pickles side is also fantastic and is the perfect addition to a scrumptious burger Overall I love DMK Burger Bar Its a great casuallyhip restaurant that I always recommend to friends when they are in Chicago Definitely worth the trip Proud to say that I am now a member of the DMK Rewards Club

Author: Alexandria T.
Content: My boyfriend  I came here after a show at the Vic on a Saturday night about a month ago  They were able to seat us in about ten minutes because of how late in the evening it was  We were starving and were excited to score a table so quicklyThey have a fantastic beer selection and we were able to try some new brews which as beer lovers is always a plus  This was my second visit to DMK but my first since Yelping  The first time I didnt love it but I was more than willing to give it a second go because of all of the hype  I ordered the veggie burger without any changes  We also ordered the Wisconsin cheddar and scallion fries  The server immediately disclosed that the fries are not vegetarian because they are cooked in some type of animal fat  Im not super super strict so I am ok with this and I really appreciated her honesty about the potentially questionably ingredientsOur food came out quickly which was great because I was starving  Once again I was very disappointed by the veggie burger  It has a soggy consistency and the flavor falls way too short for all of the hype this place receives  My favorite part of my meal was the fries  I definitely wouldnt wait to eat here for over an hour and I probably wont be back because there are many other places in the city that have awesome veggie burgers

Author: Hersh A.
Content: Go here for good tasty burgers their nice flavored house sodas and thick rich  creamy milkshakes I enjoyed all of that on my 1st visit recently If you like lamb try their lamb burger 11 I liked the taziki sauce  feta cheese combo Try their PineappleBasil soda  Espresso milkshake as well The milkshake flavor was super delicious I loved the drinks I had  I also liked their sweet potato fries  onion strings Good menu variety The ambiance is okay  A bit too noisy for my liking and a bit pricey as well But its definitely worth a visit 35 stars

Author: Liz C.
Content: I live right by DMK and go there a bunch Whenever I am craving a burger and fries this is my goto spot I have a frequent diner card so it is about time I write a review  Honestly all DMK restaurants do it right  I specifically love Ada St and DMK burger bar  The staff are always attentive knowledgeable and honestly the shit  They just take care of the customer and make it a good experienceMy favorite burgers are probably the 5 and 6 the bison and chorizo burgers And the friesso damn good  Dont go in there and not order fries  Love the sweet potato ones and the truffle parmesan ones are amazing tooLets not forget about those shakes  Even when I dont think I will really like it they change my mind  One time the special was a carmel corn shake for some reason Im not huge on carmeland it converted meEven if youre not in the neighborhood hit DMK up  It has bangin burgers fries beer and shakes

Author: Sylvia C.
Content: Looks like this place has been reviewed to death so I will say thisAmish Blue and Smoked bacon fries Thats a meal by itself and decadently heavyTheir burgers are solid I had the lamb bison and one with egg I have to say the blueberry comes out in the bison burger and with the goat cheese and meat was a fantastic flavor combo

Author: Anthony H.
Content: Burger 4 Roasted Hatch Green Chile Fried Farm Egg Sonoma Jack Smoked Bacon Awesome combo to say the least Ive been here multiple times and the service has always been great This month their special was a black bean chili which you can add as a topping on anything for only a buck extra Instinctively ordered that on their Wisconsin Cheddar  Scallion fries Sooo gooood

Author: Denzell W.
Content: DMK is without a doubt my favorite place to get a burger in Chicago Its usually about a 2530 minute wait to get in but its well worth it The selection of beer is great the variety of burgers is from Bison  Crab  BBQ The music servers seating everything makes sense hereGreat for a group of friends or a first date laidback

Author: Frankie C.
Content: I have been to DMK Burger a couple times before and the service keeps getting better Service I have always had spectacular service here Marie is my fav server hands down Also the GM Michael is such a doll Food They have one burger and one beer that they rotate on the menu so you can try something new each time you go There is never a long wait once you place your order Quality unmatched Their wide beer selection is a huge bonus Ambiance Fantastic layout Just want a beer go to the bar Want to sit down and enjoy a bison burger nom nom you can also do that too Cost Factor On par with other burger bars Overall FABULOUS

Author: Nicole J.
Content: DMK just continues to get it right This has become my favorite place in the city for a weekend meal Burgers are delicious quality grass fed yumminess and on the thinner side the way I prefer They also make their own buns bonus points which are perfect and thin enough to not take away from the overall burger but also to allow you to actually take a bite without the fillings spilling out Double bonus points for the amazing sauces and eclectic toppings as well as the super delicious fries Truffle Parmesan are the bomb We also like to order the deviled eggs as an app ten times better than your mom makes I promiseOh and triple bonus points for the amazingly prompt kind and attentive servers they are the icing on the cake Best burger bar hands down

Author: Amy W.
Content: We had scheduled Franks n Dawgs for today sadly we looked online and they are closed Mondays so we were denied  We decided we needed a sammy or a burger and this was in the neighborhood with good reviews so we hiked in the falling snow to get thereThere were 3 burgers I was focused on  either the pastrami burger the hatch green chili burger or the Lamb burger I decided to go lamb only bc it is more unusual to find on a menu  Then we decided on a large truffle fries and the onion strings  our lovely waitress Patience thats her name offer to get us just a 12 order of the onion strings since we were ordering a lot that is not offered on the menu  so a super nice touch  The lamb burger was with cucumber feta and olive tapenade It tasted like a gyro burger and a damn fine choice loved it  My friend got the patty melt  Really good but a bit greasy Bacon was nice and thickly cut  As we were finishing our meal a nice waiter came by with a split of a strawberry shake in 2 glasses  saying Patience sent this to us a a special treat  It was the special shake of the month and it was great I cant remember the last time I had a shake but it sure was creamy and fresh strawberry tastingApparently these folks own Ada Street which I loved and  fish place next door too

Author: John V.
Content: I absolutely love DMK I usually get the bacon cheeseburger with truffle fries bartenders and wait staff are very friendly its sometimes pricier then other burger places but the food is top notch I always enjoy visiting DMK with friends Great job to all

Author: Miguel C.
Content: Just another burger place but a pretty good oneThe location and decor are excellent  I love the large chalk board letting you know what beers are available  Nothing quite like a good beer and a good burger  I had the big DMK burger which I enjoyed thoroughly  Make sure to get some fries as well theyve got a few options all of which are delicious

Author: Sabra R.
Content: 10 stars  So this is actually my third review  I was in Chicago on business and drove 25 minutes to DMK two nights in a row  The second night I decided to take a burger home to my other half so she could experience bliss once again she hadnt had one in over 2 years  I ended up ordering 4two 10s for me and a 1 and 3 for her  The bartender was amazingshe packed all of the wet items condiments and lettuce and tomatoes separately so the bread wouldnt get soggy in transit  Oh yeah forgot to mention that I live in DC and planned to take the burgers on my flight the following day  I got almost all the way back to the hotel when I realized that Id forgotten to order her burgers with turkey instead of beef  She eats beef but the turkey is just otherworldly  SO i actually turned around drove 20 mins BACK on the highway just to order a double turkey burger so she could switch out her beef  Crazy  No  Obbessed  Perhaps  The turkey burgers are just that damn  good  One day one city 615 miles and 85 dollars later the turkey burgers are STILL the best we have ever had   Ok this is my last review  But I need the Head Chef to call me or write me  I MUST HAVE THIS RECIPE  I promise not to share  We just cant wait another year for this magic

Author: Radha K.
Content: I love DMK Its a great place to grab drinks and its burgers are pretty incredible The chorizo burger is my personal favorite but the bison burger is just as good You really cant go wrong heregreat beer and great food The atmosphere is greatgreat music Great service I just love it

Author: Erica S.
Content: I love burgers and I love meat At DMK I seriously had the best veggie burger of all time Made with brown rice and veggies and cheese that melts in your mouth this is a meal Ill have to come back for just to satisfy my craving Even better the prices are super decent 9 for my burger Fries are extra on the side but so worth it sweet potato are to die forThe servers are super nice and friendly they have great beer on tap and make their own crafty cocktails What more could you want

Author: Jenny N.
Content: The truffle sauce is a must haveBurgers were flawlessenvironment was niceThe place gets pack very quicklyThe only flaw was not enough staff

Author: P T.
Content: Burgers were ok not the best ever and certainly not worth the price  In addition this place is too LOUD to have any kind of conversation  I will NOT return

Author: Sarah S.
Content: Wow Wow Wow My boyfriend and I visited DMK Burger Bar about a week ago during a short getaway to see the Cubs We stopped in DMK Burger Bar after finding an ad for it in our hotel magazine After reading some reviews we decided to goThe place was packed but conveniently enough there were two seats at the bar We were immediately greeted by the bartender Andrew He was SO knowledgable about the beers they offered AND the menu Since we were new to the place he had no problem tour guiding us to find something we both would love We started off with the Fried Okra and Pickles They were awesome For our dinner we split the Turkey Burger and decided to pay 1 extra for an over easy egg We were both left speechless DMK Burger Bar offers a great young atmosphere and spectacular service  food Oh and not to mention their ticket times Our food arrived quickly and the food runner was very helpful as well Being as though my boyfriend and I are both bartenders and servers we couldnt get over how seamless this experience was Everything was perfect from start to finish We even liked it so much that on our last day there we stopped in for a round of drinks before we ran to catch our flight DMK Burger Bar is MUST

Author: Joseph D.
Content: I guess burgers are such a personal thing that with DMK youre gonna either love it or hate it I guess I fall on the love it side Burgers are all interesting combos and come served patty style meaning youre not going to get the big thick honking burger you might find at the little joint down the street  But theres nothing saying you couldnt go all double meat and load up on protein Just sayingThe fries were pretty darn tasty Smothered in cheese and I want to say truffle oil Delicious the beer selection is also quite good has to be in a burger joint and the service top notch The place was jammed and yet we still had excellent service As we were new to the place Jack our server even gave us a free app of friend pickles Nice tough and much appreciated They also offer shakes in which I did not indulge as the burgers and beers had me already feeling satisfied Next time perhapsTry it and Im sure youll like it

Author: Mary S.
Content: Being a nonmeat eater I was weary to try this place because of the massive amount of beef burgers floating around The menu does claim to have the best damn veggie burgers so I figured Id give them a tryWith that I tried 12 the house veggie and grain burger with eggplant I had read a few reviews already here saying that even for meateaters this was the best veggie burger theyd ever had UhhhhIm not sure what other veggie burgers theyve tried but this wasnt what I would consider the best The patty itself was okgood but not goodgreat that would have to go to Kumas And the eggplant that I received on the burger was two slices the size of a silver dollar I mean if youre going to say the burger has eggplant on it let me have some It honestly kind of just tasted like something I could have made at home with a patty out of the freezer section of Jewel The bun was seriously sad and the burger itself wasnt anything to write home about It was still good but dont think Id go back for anotherI also tried to sweet potato fries which typically I dont like sweet potato fries but there were definitely great I would go back just for the fries not the burgers Also tried the Parmesan truffle fries equally as amazing Unfortunately all of their fries are made with some type of beef fat or beef butter as we were told by the waitress thanks for the heads up but I figured Id give them a try anyway My stomach revolted later that night because of that maybe I wont be going back for the fries thenOverall this really is just meant for meat eaters They are trying to meet the needs of everyone I get it but their veggie options fall flat

Author: Timothy T.
Content: DMK is a solid spot for a beer and a burger  The staff is very nice and knowledgable the ambiance is relaxed and the food is delicious  Theres something for everyone on their menu that changes frequently  The beer list is extensive and even their housemade sodas are good

Author: Brian S.
Content: Solid burger place wait wasnt that long 10 minutesThe food came out super fast We order the 1 and 6 with truffle fries cheddar fries and fried picklesFood tasted great Fries were fantastic as well Afterwards  we ordered the shamrock shake which was also amazing Definitely recommend

Author: Daniele N.
Content: This is a December  Tuesday night reviewPeople at this place was super dooooper friendly  Fresh young and prompt staff   for the guys the waitresses are smoking hot  girls dont be afraid they are hot but very professional  lolNow on a serious note I absolutely love the food  Good consistent and delicious hamburger  Not your traditional bun but I thought it was a million times better  I chose the 5 which comes with goat cheese bison meat and pickled onions  We also had a side of sweet potato fries  Although the burger is not huge it was the right size for my hunger  My husband had the 4 which I had a bite and was delicious as well  The mix of flavor is amazing the food just melted inside my mouth  For now on this will be  1 place to go for a healthier version burger when Im craving this type of food Staff was attentive  My burger fist came without the goat cheese but I immediately told the smokin hot good teethnicesmileandboobs waitress lol and within minutes she came back with my burger fixed  Not only that someone showed up with a complimentary peanutbutter milk shake right then  HUmmmmm nice way to fix up your act guys lol Im very satisfied with food and service will recommend this place and will be back for sure

Author: Seher D.
Content: Scene It was Tuesday night at 11 PM My mom and sister were visiting me and we had all just attended a story slam not too far away To our excitement my sandbox sistah and I were chosen as judges of the stories during The Moth and used all of our energy and brain power to score semimediocre and notsoclean stories sadly The Moth in Chicago doesnt compare to its counterpart in New York We were starving and decided to reward ourselves with some good eats and luckily DMK was still open  Before my sisters arrival we had compiled a Google Doc of all the places we had wanted to try However DMK was a spontaneous destination and it did not disappoint We were immediately seated and our waitress was amazingly nice She recommended her favorite burgers and gave us a short blurb about each one  4 and 6 were her favorites but she continued to go on and on about DMKs veggie burger 12 Veggie burger At a place known for its grassfed beef I was perplexed  We went ahead and ordered the 6 sans the chorizo with guac Sonoma Jack cheese chipotle aioli cilantro and onions and the 12 veggie burger with aged cheddar eggplant tomato and pesto mayo Both were delicious The patty is thin but definitely high quality Although Im a huge fan of thick juicy patties these DMK patties were still pretty good but I still would have preferred a thicker patty However what really makes the burger good is the combination of toppingsingredients Everything went together so well and the flavors were delicious Do not underestimate this veggie burger Even my carnivore sister couldnt get enough of it   We also ordered a side of mac  cheese 1 and parmesan  truffle cream fries The mac  cheese was AMAZING Great combination of aged cheddar and parmesan and a great crust on top that adds some texture Its definitely really rich but if youre a mac  cheese fan dont pass this up BUT THAT TRUFFLE CREAM OMG When it came out my traditional mom didnt know what was happening White ketchup Is this like when Heinz tried to make green ketchup But once my mom tried it she was basically eating it plain It was that good  Finally to finish off our meal some lovely gentleman at the bar bought everyone a small sample of their pecan pie milkshake Was this the equivalent of getting bought a drink at da klub Since my mom was present Im glad the drink was sans alcohol And mann was this a tasty milkshake As a Southern girl I love me some pecan pie and in a milkshake Even better Ill definitely be back for this cause I couldnt get enough If only I could order it at da klub

Author: Daniel C.
Content: I love DMK burger barThey have 14 burger options with a 15th monthly specialI havent tried EVERY burger here but I have tried a good 10 at leastThe flavor combinations are really inventive The special is usually something really out of the box  Try the bison burger They also have salmon turkey lamb and portabello as options for the BurgerThey have brunch burgers which sound amazing but I havent made it over there to try them yet They have a huge selection of beers and homemade sodasThey also pick a charity each month to donate to which is listed on their website under giving

Author: Mary L.
Content: Went with a group of 4 after a long day out and about and everyone felt that the food here really hit the spot  Even though we had to wait about 2025 minutes to be seated the host was attentive and the food came out quickly  Burgers are great quality and simple not overloaded with too many toppings  Definitely one of the best burger spots in the city

Author: Cristina P.
Content: This place just always nails it for me I came back and had the brunch burger that has scrambled eggs and chilaquiles  So dang good and just the right amount of heat  Also ordered salt and pepper fries which were so simple but so tasty  How can just pepper taste so good

Author: Sarah M.
Content: Servers are fantastic and Ive never had a bad burger either Highly recommend the mac and cheese both or the wisconsin cheddar fries Great beer list

Author: Lisette D.
Content: I wouldnt say the burger here was anything more than OK How does a place that focuses on burgers not ask how you want it done Our burgers were thin and somewhere between well done and medium well but it was too dark to know for certain I understand that the burgers are from all grass fed cows but these were not worth 11 each They had a decent beer list but not much on tap the best stuff was in bottles I liked that they had fried pickles and okra which were probably the best thing we had The sweet potato fries were lackluster but the bacon and bluecheese fries were tasty  I did like that they donate some proceeds to different charities every month However it was so loud that when the waitress described what charity and what food items were involved I couldnt hear what she said I wont be going out of my way to go to this place again I could get just as tasty a burger although with less fancy toppings for half the price at Five Guys

Author: Kris G.
Content: I held off on writing a review for this location because I liked the Lombard atmosphere and staff better Needless to say the setup and staff have won me over at this location and now I love it This is easily my goto restaurant for any burger or french fry craving my two favorite foodsIve ended up at DMK twice after going to bars The first was after a trip to Headquarters down the street and the second time was last night after I first visited Barrelhouse Flat My bf and I ordered the poutine at Barrelhouse Flat and my bf mentioned I wish DMK brought out fries in a large bowl like this I would be lying if I said we DIDNT spend the rest of our time at Barrelhouse waiting to finish our drinks and get the check so we could walk over to DMKWhen we did make it to DMK we ordered our favorites the 4 and salt and pepper fries and devoured them in record time Not only that but we did this for a fraction of what we paid for food alone at Barrelhouse Perfectly cooked burgers DELICIOUS fries I wish I could DMK every day

Author: Ryan M.
Content: With nearly 1200 reviews I dont think there is much I could say to add to the fanfare written about this lovely establishment But here are my additional 2 cents because well I want to give themI recently started eating meat again after 5 years of being pescetarian look it up As a good friend describes it Im a recovering vegetarian I had a few meals at home but decided it was time to reintroduce my dining self to meat DMK looked like the perfect placeThe burgers grassfed and antibioticfree come in many varieties as do the fries and the milkshakes and so on I started things right with the Number 5  Bison goat cheese and blueberry BBQ sauce HOLY SHIT My taste buds were so happy with me I do not know if words can describe the wonderful combination of flavors Nor will I try But I will recommend getting the Number 5I returned a few weeks later and tried the Number 4 again with Bison even though it normally is ground beef what can I say Im sticking with the original  Roasted green chilies a fried egg jack cheese and smoked bacon HOLY SHIT AGAIN Lets just say I have at least 12 more visits to go there are that many normal options plus specials Sweet LordAdd to that the tasty music playing nottooloudly in the background some DAMN tasty sweet potato fries the lemon aioli that comes with is spectacular and a very chill atmosphere and youve got one of my new favorite places And BONUS If you do not eat meat they have a veggie burger you can swap in for beef same for a portobello Stomach love

Author: Dave J.
Content: While I wouldnt consider DMK among the best burgers in the city the thin griddled burgers are certainly a welcome change  Ive got a major bone to pick with any place that serves a 4 thick patty with a steak knife skewer  Its a burger not a meatballThat being said DMK only cooks their burgers two temperatures which equates to well and really well  The patty melt was not lacking for flavor but it didnt really satisfy my craving for a really good burger  Perhaps its unfair but any place I have a burger will be judged against The Bad Apple and thats a pretty tall orderThe beer list was fine and the sweet potato fries and mac  cheese were pretty stellar  I couldnt quite get past the atmosphere and clientele though  It was kind of like eating at a fancy frat house At the end of the day I didnt feel like Id be running back to DMK but the food still warrants four stars  I guess youll have to see for yourself

Author: Avengers M.
Content: Totally worth the five month wait I have been waiting to be in Chicago for a weekend to try this place and it was awesome Great wait staff and the food was amazing Parmesan fires were the best They also have specials to keep it fresh

Author: Ali K.
Content: Been dying to hit up DMK and finally got my way visiting my friends A few of my friends who live in Chicago had been telling me this place along with Kumas is one of the best burger joints around A friend of mine who is in the hospitality industry was able to set up this dinner with a few surprise perks thrown in as well but that even if those extra perks didnt occur the service here was excellent Waitress was very bubbly and talkative gorgeous with a ton of crazy unique tattoos I loved every second of it A ton of people were in there and the kitchen still managed to get our food out in under 15 minutes which was awesome I ordered the 4 Burger which had Roasted Hatch Green Chile Fried Farm Egg Sonoma Jack Smoked Bacon on it Very interesting flavor profile and it tasted absolutely superb I would have expected it to be hotter but it really wasnt bad at all A fried egg always helps out any burger We also got a bunch of french fries for the table we tried the Wisconsin Cheddar Scallion Parmesan w Truffle Cream and the Sweet Potato Fries Surprisingly the best ones were the Wisconsin Cheddar Scallion they just burst with flavor and the Sweet Potato ones were pretty good The Parmesan Fries w Truffle Cream was good to but didnt blow me away Surprisingly the Mac and Cheese 2 was very very very good it has Gruyere Cheese Smoked Bacon Charred Balsamic Red Onions very unique  Also on the house we were given Peanut Butter Milkshakes were which the icing on the cake it was so so so good Friendly staff great vibe awesome food This place should open up locations in a few major cities Im sure they would be successful hell if they wanted me to be a part of the team to open multiple nationwide locations I would do it thats how good they are

Author: Vicki N.
Content: Was looking online for a Burger place near me for me mostly vegetarian and my boyfriend very into healthy food and was intrigued by the fact that the beef is grassfedThe atmosphere is a bit hipster and modern not as cozy as I was expecting and it was quite crowded and a little loud  but thats to be expected with a place so wellknown and with so many great reviews  The waitstaff is friendly and very casual which was very nice but really the food makes the placeThe fries and burgers here are amazing  One can substitute the main component in any burger I went with Fried Portobello in 12 with Aged Cheddar Eggplant Tomato and Pesto Mayo  He had the 4 doublestacked Roasted Hatch Green Chile Fried Farm Egg Sonoma Jack Smoked Bacon and we shared the Amish Blue  Smoked Bacon fries which were absolutely deliciousOverall amazing food and good price  The atmosphere is more pub  barlike and while I didnt have any drinks their cocktails sounded quite good  I would definitely go again to try more food and drinks  Thumbs up

Author: Kelly D.
Content: Checked out this place a couple weeks agoAOKWe got there late night and I did like that they had a special late night menu in addition to regular menu  Late night menu had smaller portions of a few burgers shakes etc which was nice cause I wanted to try the shake but wanted to beer to go with the burgerEnded up getting the lamb burger which was AMAZING Tasted like everything you would order in greek town smashed on a bunolives feta lamb tzatziki and cukessoooo good We also ordered the green chile burgermeh Not a ton of spice which is surprising cause I figured itd have a kick from the chiles and the bacon was terriblehard as shoe leather I couldnt even tear it apart to taste it  I also thought the burger patties themselves were a bit thinmaybe 2 sliders patties thick Milk shakes were very tastypersonally Id recommend the peanut butter one if you stop by  Not expensive at all2 burgers 2 small shakes and a beer was like 35bucksWould probably return but wouldnt go out of my way

Author: Amanda C.
Content: Pretty decent place I was the first to walk in so I was in and out in 20 min Ordered the bison burger with a fried egg First time having a bison and as the server said it was beefy flavored YumMy only gripe here are the prices The burger is petite and didnt come with fries With tax it was 1314 Although I do like not walking out too full it was a bit much for the portion

Author: Adam E.
Content: Happy to have this great option in my hood Plus the staff is stellar Seriously stellarIve had almost every burger on the menu and have yet to be disappointed  My favorite was the old 5 and now the bison burger For fries you cant go wrong with the bacon and blue cheese fries  I think this was one of two bacon experiences that started to really get that going for me coming from my baconfree upbringing  I kept kosher for 22 years it happensBeer selection is always good they are always able to make good suggestions and are happy to offer small samples  And it never fails which always helpsThe burgers arent as oversized and massive as some places but I kind of like that I feel like I dont have to be wheeled out after enjoying every last bite And if you are there on a sunny afternoon for lunch I have to suggest the peanut butter milkshakes I took my parents there for lunch once and the server brought them over free of charge and they were great

Author: Lindsay M.
Content: I dont understand the hypeI am with my fellow Yelp love here Brett D I didnt love it and I didnt hate it  Its just kinda meh  which is why this one is just a 3star rating for meI have to say I like this location MUCH better than the location I have been to in the suburbsThe meat doesnt really taste all that great and the burger combos are decent but nothing to write home about Actually I can say that about everything here Nothing to write home about

Author: Aaron Jae M.
Content: This place really does make tasty burgers and friesThey have a selection of 15 burgers at all times and 5 types of friesBurgers do not come with friesI tried the 8 burger which is just a classic burger and it was deliciousPerfectly cooked with tasty ingredients on top and a good bunWe got the classic fries with just salt and pepper and tried the Wisconsin cheddar fries with scallions The cheese fries were good but the cheese was not very evenly distributed so some fries were all cheese and others just tasted like the regular friesWe ordered 2 larges to share between the table 5 people and finished maybe half of each since we were all too invested in our burgersThis place also has a very good craft beer selection which we took full advantage ofI have heard great things about their milkshakes and will most likely be back to try one out along with another burger

Author: Hannah S.
Content: VEGETARIANSBEWARE THEIR FRIES ARE DONE UP IN BEEF FATOur first visit my boyfriend and I came for dinner and loved it I had the crispy portobello veggie burger and he had something beefy bacony and smothered in onions We shared a milkshake and the sweet potato  truffle fries in blissful ignorance On our second visit I tried the veggie patty and went to order some fries when our waitress KINDLY told me that they fry their fries in beef fat This is NO WHERE on the menu Having eaten the fries before after ordering a veggie burger and not being informed that they are fried in fat I was absolutely horrified It was a really heartbreaking experience I am so disappointed in DMK for not being more transparent about this fact and for inadvertently breaking my commitment Had they told me off the bat I would have given the restaurant 45 stars Their veggie burgers are truly wonderful but the fry incident really made me sad Shame on you guys DMK

Author: Shaye R.
Content: I keep wanting to like this place but I always end up being lessthanimpressed by the burgersPros Amazingly delicious appetizers  sides They use grassfed beef Pretty friendly staff Cool atmosphere although loudCons House Burgers on the menu are meh  Ive tried about 4 different kinds and theyre underwhelming  Also on busy nights theyve messed up my orderSide note Fish Bar next door although small is more my flavor

Author: Chris J.
Content: One of the best burgers I had in a long time Staff was helpful and attentive Christa one of my servers was super cool too I definitely will be back the staff is trained  and the food was awesome and reasonable Thanks so much DMK

Author: Joe M.
Content: Girlfriend and I visited DMK Burger bar for the first time last weekend prior to a show at the VicNormally I write a longwinded detailed review to try and help paint a picture to the reader and aide them in their decision of what business to support and which to kick to the curbnot this timeI am a fish and chicken kinda guy I am no burger connoisseur by any means but Ive had a lot of burgers from a lot of different placesthe burgers at DMK are in a class of their own  Never had a burger that comes close to the awesomeness that I experienced here  Girlfriend ordered the 4 I ordered the 1 both of which we found out after the factbartender said were two of the most popular along with 5  We also ordered the parmesan  white truffle friesBartender was attentive and friendly atmosphere of restaurant was good found some of the patrons to be a bit pretentious and casting judgy glances but who gives a shit  The burgers here will change all your perceptions and like a glorious miracle from the heavenschange your life for the better

Author: Lindsay D.
Content: DMK has definitely grown on me I wasnt a fan at first but now I really enjoy going   It is very noisy which is one of the downfalls and the wait can also be very long especially since you cant make reservations It is best to come with 2 people and sit at the bar  fast service easier to talk with the person you come with and everyone who works behind the bar is very friendlyMy all time favorite thing from DMK is their milkshake it is the best Ive ever hadI really enjoy the wedge salad  The avocado salad also looks deliciousThe Bears Burger with pulled pork on top was my favorite burger

Author: Alexandra C.
Content: One of my favorite places to grab a burger in Chicago Laid back casual atmosphere and the staff is great Their macaroni and cheese fries and turkey burgers are the best

Author: Michael P.
Content: I have zero complaints about this place FOR WHAT IT IS  I rate places based on how successful they are at what theyre trying to be  DMK is more about the toppings and flavors than the burger  If you want a big fat inchthink patty that aint what youre going to get here cause thats not what theyre trying to do  The patty is a vehicle for packages of flavor  And its not like the patties are bad  They are fine theyre just not the star of the show and theyre not meant to be  My visit there last Saturday was around my 10th time there  I have never walked out unhappy  My date and I each got a whiskey cocktail hers a little better than mine but both were good especially considering the price  For eats we ordered the 3 with pastrami gruyere and kraut the 4 with fried egg roasted green chiles sonoma jack and bacon  and the deep fried pickle spears  As a bonus the waitress brought us the parm truffle fries  Dont know if they were an extra order or a mistake in the kitchen or what and who cares  The burgers tasted great they are big enough to satisfy unless youre a pig or a linebacker the pickles are great though Id prefer chips and the fries were great free or not  Again I get it if you like a thicker burger  You can go somewhere else and get that  And youll end up paying another 35 more for a burger with toppings like you get at DMK  And youll wait for your food longer  And the other joint probably isnt donating a percentage of its receipts to a local charity every month

Author: Chris B.
Content: Always a great meal  We like to sit at the bar if you can grab a seat as the bartenders are great  Very friendly and know their stuff  Effie is a friendly face and took great care of us  I had my goto the 11 and my wife tried the 1 for the first time both were exceptional  Love this place

Author: Chris J.
Content: Consistently very good I dont like the French fry options but the burger and bison burgers will not disappoint Fairly loud

Author: Pedro L.
Content: Its no Kumas Ive never been to Kumas but I like saying that  You annoying saying  I ate the Chorizo burger shared onion strings  fried okra  Pretty good  Not the best burger in the city but by no means does that mean to writeoff this place  Its basically an upscale steak and shake  Bartender must have had an off day or was deceivingly greedy  Kept forgetting to give change back  Im not tipping you 12 for 1 beer  Ill be back here to eat if Im in the area and the wait isnt too long

Author: Hannah J.
Content: I enjoy the food here but the atmosphere is not for people who like a quiet welllit dinner with personal space It is a fun place to go for a burger and the prices are reasonable but they could turn up the lights and put more space between tables You have to yell to hear the person across from you and move your table to get in and out of your seat so you dont bump the table next to you That said I do like their burgers and the sweet potato fries were amazing

Author: Eric H.
Content: They have good burgers and fries here but the portions are kind of lacking for the price Its a little bit overpriced but I guess thats mainly because of the neighborhood Service is very good and the food comes out quickly

Author: A M.
Content: 220 Juicy lucy  great very rich Ceddar fries a bit salty for my taste Fried Dill and okra is great to start Wife had the 2 prepared with the veggie burger pattyThe bar is great with plenty of wellprepared craft cocktailsLove this place

Author: Chris W.
Content: Not too bad 35 bucks for two people two burgers a large fry to split Wisconsin Cheddar a nice choice with just enough cheese that we were able to get some on every fry on the plate a peanut butter and oreo shake and a blood orange house sodaThe blood orange soda was WAY better than I was expecting and the shakes proceeds went to charity I was a little bummed that the burgers didnt come with fries and the plates they were on were so small that if youre a messy eater like I am its kind of a struggle not to get food everywhere However the food itself made up for every little nit picking detail that I didnt like Like how we could have used a few extra napkins and the server didnt really attend to us very oftenPretty loud in there and super trendy I felt underdressed honestly Ill be back though Theyre on par with Kumas in my opinion and their selection is extensive They also have a changing monthly special The number 15 I think which last month was the fajita burger which blew my taste buds AND my mind 45 stars for DMK

Author: Sarah D.
Content: Four stars for the sweet potato fries and the milkshakes but only two stars for the burger I had the number 5 and found it bland despite the toppings I had to add more bbq sauce and even that didnt help much I had high hopes since one of my best friends swears by this place but for me it just didnt satisfy

Author: Amanda M.
Content: Awesome place Their Grassfed natural burgers were amazing and so were their sweet potato fries Our waitress was super nice too Definitely recommend

Author: Mike P.
Content: It was okay I understand the rave reviews if youre accustomed to eating fast food burgers This place is definitely better than that Although I feel that there are better burger places in Chicago  Had the their Green Chile burger and the table split the fries with scallions The burger itself was thin and Im guessing thats why we werent asked how we wanted the burger cooked  The flavor was good but really not up to the level I would have expected The fries were quite good though Ill try it again at some point Could have been a bad day

Author: Patricia K.
Content: Ive had wonderful experiences here both for lunch and dinner Stopped in for lunch before a near by appointment and we sat at the bar the two of us split a cider and ordered the lamb burger and patty melt as well as sweet potato fries and fried okra As we were waiting our bartender Parkerover heard us talking about how we worked in the service industry and brought us some French frie samples as well as some beer tastings loved it The sweet potato fries are AWESOME We split our burgers very happy Super pleased with service Came back to meet a friend for an early dinner had to get the sweet potato fries Burgers were good service was good over all good experience

Author: Nikki C.
Content: The staff is once again a shining star as in all of the DMK places Ive been lucky to tryAttentive well schooled in the menu and specials and just genuinely nice people you would enjoy to have at your next BBQThe place itself can use a little more soft fabric or sound treatment to cut down on the loudness the place can achieve but still a good place to take a group of friends or family you can standThe food is tasty The fries truffle oil sweet potato blue cheese n bacon are awesomebut this in part to being fried in animal fatwhich I much enjoyThe burgers for which this place is named is grass fed and tasty My issue is the bun to meat ratio which is unbalanced for my taste and only corrected when  you upgrade to a double or more or just forgo the top bun and go open facedSometimes Ill just order a single and slice it in half but double stack the meat from the other side making the meat to bun ratio more to my personal liking and the veggie options of bean or portabello burgers are incredible even for a carnivoreIll get a veggie burger with bacon sometimesThe beers and cocktails are awesome and well complemented by the milkshakes which finish off any carnivorous outing like OH HELL YES GoodnessJoin their free DMK points program and earn enough points for freebie sides and tasty meals

Author: Brian K.
Content: Best burger Not by a longshot The meat patty doesnt cover the bun and its drowned with toppings The taste of balsamic vinegar was essentially the burger Would you like some burger with your vinegarThe meat patty is smashed to death intentionally like a Smash Burger patty The result is a burger that isnt too moistThe sweet potato fries with spicy aioli was good as was the service and limited but curated beer selection DMK would be a cool place to hang out with drinks but not for burgers Save your calories and money 9 plus taxtip for a burger

Author: Stacy S.
Content: Loooove DMK I could eat their turkey burgers every day of my life Their Mac n Cheese WI Cheddar fries and Sweet Potato fries are also delicious They have great seasonal drinks as well Its great for take out Join their rewards program I got a free tshirt

Author: Steven M.
Content: Solid burger  Got the number 4 and was very happy  I was a concerned that the green chilies might be a little overwhelming but they werent spicy so it worked out perfectlyThe Amish blue and smoked bacon fries were tremendous in taste not size because I got the small one and I would definitely do that again if there werent other also goodsounding fries on the menu  The creaminess and bacon make it feel like youre enjoying a fingereatable baked potatowhich is I guess almost exactly what it is

Author: Jen J.
Content: I ordered the 4 Roasted Hatch Green Chile with the Parmesan fries with truffle cream The total was pricey but the burger was cheaper than Kumas However I thought the burger was just okay I wanted to try DMK because Im a burger fan and this place had such great reviews Maybe ill try a different burger and see but for now I prefer Kumas burgers in terms of taste and quality The fries were really good though

Author: Jay R.
Content: I have been to DMK numerous times but this is my first review After many burgers and fries eaten I have to say DMK is AOK and that A stands for AwesomeThe burgers are unique with a great balance of flavors and toppingsThey know how to work a fryer like they where born with one out of the wombGreat variety of beers I had The Dogfish Head Midas Touch and Founders KBS People who like beer they will appreciate the beer list from these 2 selections alone  Staff and service is fabulousContrary to earlier post they will modify one of their burger to how ever we wanted itCool atmosphere inside Sign up for rewards program you actually get free foodFree protected password WiFi  like working from home but with a bar and restaurant in my living roomMust tryTruffle Parmesan Fries  perfectly fried great truffle dipping sauceFried Pickles and Okra  again perfectly fried great flavors and dipping sauceIf you not drinking beer get a  shake  Coffee shake had texture with chopped roasted beans was to goodBig DMK was a spin on the Big Mac was really good and huge

Author: Meghan H.
Content: Oh nelly I reeeeally love DMKIve only been there once and I am IN LOVE Love at first bite if you will  AnnnnywaysI got the patty melt Lets break it down burger perfect thickness thin but not too thin big ol slice of swiss bacon nice and crunchy but not so much so that it falls apart into powdercrumbs as you eat it plus good flavor just fatty enough but not overly so with a nice subtle peppery taste to it AND to top it all off a fried egg that was perfectly cooked so that the burger wasnt ridiculously messy AND burnt onions  that were so deliciously caramelized without an overkill oniony tasteyum all on some perfectlytoasted rye bread Whewww This burger warrants a grammatically incorrect runon sentence Id sayNow I also tried out their mac and cheese and found that cheeseilymoist though in need of a bit more flavor as the cheese taste could have been a weebit more pronounced BUT the ovenbaked crunchy part on top of the mac was very goodWe also ordered their parmesan and truffle oil fries to share and those paired beautifully with me burger DelishWhat made this experience even more grand was when our waitress brought us complimentary blood orange sodas D It felt super random but awesome nonetheless And they were pretty good  They definitely looked nice colorwise and tasted refreshing  like jazzed up seltzer water In a good way Loved that it was not overly sweetAtmosphere Decidedly a cross between urbanindustrial and trendymod Very niiiice This place is generally pretty packed and not super great if you have a huge party itll work of course youll probably just have to wait because the place isnt too big and most of the tables are hightop barish tables that seat like 2 If you do end up having to wait itll be way worth it I really love DMK That is all

Author: Dennis F.
Content: Been some time since my last visit heredont have an excuse didnt check in on last two visits Glad I returned My friend and I were seated immediately at a great table Being a waiter I like to watch the rhythm of other restaurants The staff have a clean prompt relaxed manner perfect for the venue Started with the Chili special enough for two to share The food is a sweet change to the burger and fries lunch Had to splurge and added the Gruyere mac and cheesedamn good Looking forward to returning

Author: Jessica E.
